{"comments":"Canvas Guide Types — Ruler guides, configuration, and bounds.\n\n## Scope\n\nThis module defines types for guides and canvas configuration:\n\n- **GuideOrientation**: Horizontal or vertical\n- **Guide**: A ruler guide at a specific position\n- **CanvasConfig**: Complete canvas configuration\n- **CanvasBounds**: Infinite or finite canvas bounds\n\n## Guides\n\nGuides are visual alignment aids that can be snapped to.\nThey can be horizontal or vertical and positioned in canvas coordinates.\n\n## Canvas Bounds\n\nCanvases can be infinite (pan forever) or finite (clamped to rectangle).\nDesign tools typically use infinite bounds; export/artboards use finite.\n","declarations":[{"children":[{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Record"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["id",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"String"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["orientation",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Element","Compound","Canvas","Types","Guide"],"GuideOrientation"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["position",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Number"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["color",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"String"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["locked",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Boolean"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"tag":"REmpty"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[100,19],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Element/Compound/Canvas/Types/Guide.purs","start":[100,12]},"title":"Guide"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Eq"],"Eq"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Element","Com